Shadow (GUI item property)
==========================

Creates a black drop shadow when drawing [text](Text\_(GUI\_item\_property)) on this item.

The value of this property cannot be changed at runtime.

Syntax
------

`shadow `*`flag`*

Default value
-------------

`0`

Example(s)
----------

`shadow 1`


